summary:
This a high level overview of the State of CPython interpreter and other
python interpreters. The talk will mention about the
&nbsp\_place\_holder;changes in 3.2 release and changes coming up in 3.3
release and status of Python2.7. It will also give the details of
current state of PyPy Project, IronPython project and Jython Project..
title: State of CPython and Python Ecosystem
